{"tid":1944908,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"連登感情台 負能量的集中地 亦是佛祖救世之地","createTime":"2020-03-26T17:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T18:38:24.000Z","uid":189179,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0647784051338adbe452088f7d637e49a9cf662c","tid":1944908,"uid":189179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T17:03:41.000Z","msg":"點解要唔開心，因為未從無常和相對中抽離，感情正是無常和相對的，不是叫你去完全摒棄它，而是要學會不執著，可以享受得到的喜悅，亦能承受失去的痛苦，有時感恩，無時亦不致傷心。皆因感情本是虛無而變幻不定的，正如水一樣，你永遠捉不緊它，你能做的只能順勢而行，不執不強求。<br />\n<br />\n明白到自我是自身宇宙的主宰，亦明白到人類是宇宙中的微塵，便能由世俗色相中抽離，重新掌握和支配自己的情感，不受客觀環境影響，因情得悟，由悟入空，實現感情之自由和獨立以後，便能和&quot;空空道人&quot;一樣笑看眾生，漸漸連&quot;空&quot;和&quot;自我&quot;都給拋棄，普渡眾生，體現佛性。不過，這後面的一步對諸位痴男怨女而言，實謂too advanced。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;You can search throughout the entire universe for someone who is more deserving of your love and affection than you are yourself, and that person is not to be found anywhere. You yourself, as much as anybody in the entire universe deserve your love and affection.&quot; Buddha said."},{"pid":"726a3e64fdb43fb3ff33f858f40b4b19be2f326c","tid":1944908,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T17:04:39.000Z","msg":"-.-"},{"pid":"e3c047eebbb6db96b1881d04f5f938fb4c3d401e","tid":1944908,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T17:05:24.000Z","msg":"Up乜"},{"pid":"d59507a74de2f6fa13434f53379896ea1beb23a8","tid":1944908,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5520dfc5b9000e5df82ebcf85ee2f84b7f3c11e","tid":1944908,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T17:07:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a62985768fd61471120723a2fb931e499e511848","tid":1944908,"uid":307720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T18:27:38.000Z","msg":"樓豬夢遊緊"},{"pid":"64a7ddae8a1c13acfa40160c2d9499fe85b8f9a9","tid":1944908,"uid":189179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a62985768fd61471120723a2fb931e499e511848","tid":1944908,"uid":307720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T18:27:38.000Z","msg":"樓豬夢遊緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T18:38:24.000Z","msg":"昔者莊周夢為胡蝶，栩栩然胡蝶也。自喻適志與！不知周也。<br />\n<br />\n俄然覺，則蘧蘧然周也。不知周之夢為胡蝶與？胡蝶之夢為周與？<br />\n<br />\n周與胡蝶，則必有分矣。此之謂物化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人生不就是一場大夢嗎？在夢中醒、在夢中睡，在夢中悲歡離合&hellip;&hellip;。"}]}